{"id":610569,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/【立此存照】自愿申请下调工资及年终奖作为经营/","date":"2019-05-15T06:08:22Z","modified":"2019-05-15T06:08:22Z","title":"【立此存照】自愿申请下调工资及年终奖作为经营共担金","content":"<p>5月15日，据网友爆料，近期吉利汽车以“经营共担”为由（暂不明确是否因裁员压力），要求部分员工以“申请书”方式“自愿下调工资及年终奖”，下调部分将作为“经营共担金”用于抵扣部分未来的工资收入。有从吉利离职前员工同时称，吉利对有行政职务的员工，以汽车代发工资，迫使员工离职。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610570\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3eXkAA_nhX.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3eXkAA_nhX.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3eXkAA_nhX-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3eXkAA_nhX-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-610571\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3QXsAA0num.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3QXsAA0num.jpg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/D6kkO3QXsAA0num-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1019,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32327,38462,38463,15692]}